Web Services are Client Server applications that communicate over the network through HTTP Protocol and Exchange messages with SOAP, XML, JSON etc.
Two Types of Services:
1. SOAP --> XML on HTTP POST
2. REST --> Multiple Data Formats(JSON, text etc) on All HTTP Methods


JAVA Web Service Standards:
1. JAX-WS - JAVA API for XML based Services. These are the standards for implementing SOAP Based Web Services.
2. JAX-RS - JAVA API for Restful Web Serivces.

